  [Text] WENHUA DAOBAO [CULTURE HERALD], the only specialized 
culture paper, started publication on 3 January. 
  This paper, organized by the provincial cultural department, 
is a practical and service-typed weekly paper. In addition to 
introducing domestic and foreign cultural items, this paper 
provides ordinary people with various types of cultural, 
entertainment, and consumption information. 

