<F P=102>  WA0401151194 Shanghai People's Radio Network in Mandarin 
2300 GMT 25 Dec 93 </F>

<F P=103> WA0401151194 </F>
<F P=104>  Shanghai People's Radio Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Mandarin </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Summary] Wu Bangguo, member of the CPC Central Committee 
Political Bureau and secretary of the Shanghai municipal party 
committee, addressed a ceremony held by Shanghai Municipality to 
commemorate the centennial of Mao Zedong's birth on 25 December. 
Wu Bangguo said: "Since the Third Plenary Session of the 11th 
CPC Central Committee, our party has upheld and developed Mao 
Zedong Thought, and actively sought a socialist construction 
path suited to our nation's conditions; it has scored tremendous 
success in this respect. The most important thing is that it 
has finally found the path of socialism with Chinese 
characteristics, which Comrade Mao Zedong sought but failed to 
find in those days, thus enabling the formation of Comrade Deng 
Xiaoping's theory on socialism with Chinese characteristics." 

