<F P=102>  OW3012061793 Beijing XINHUA in English 0059 GMT 30 Dec 93 </F>
<F P=103> OW3012061793 </F>
<F P=104>  Beijing XINHUA </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Nanjing, December 30 (XINHUA) -- China's first law 
office to specialize in cases concerning tourism recently opened 
business in Nanjing, the capital of east China's Jiangsu 
Province. 
  The Jinling Law Firm offers services ranging from 
international tourism, foreign trade and economic cooperation to 
intellectual property rights. 
  With headquarters in Nanjing, it has set up agencies in the 
United States, Japan and Hong Kong. 
  The office aims at clients who are either domestic or 
overseas tourist agencies, or foreign tourists, investors and 
businessmen. 

