<F P=100> Economic &amp; Agricultural </F>
<H3> <TI>   Li Peng Signs Decree on Natural Resources Tax </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  OW0501000794 Beijing XINHUA Domestic Service in Chinese 2112 
GMT 27 Dec 93 </F>

<F P=103> OW0501000794 </F>
<F P=104>  Beijing XINHUA Domestic Service </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Chinese </F>
Article Type:BFN 

<F P=106> ["Decree No. 139 of the State Council of the People's </F>
Republic of China"] 
  [Text] Beijing, 28 Dec (XINHUA) -- Decree No. 139 of the 
State Council of the People's Republic of China 
  The "Provisional Regulations on Natural Resources Taxes in 
the People's Republic of China," which have been adopted at the 
12th Executive Meeting of the State Council on 26 November 1993, 
are now promulgated. They shall go into effect as of 1 January 
1994. 
  [Signed] Premier Li Peng 
  [Dated] 25 December 1993 

</TEXT>

