GMT 29 Dec 93 </F>

<F P=103> OW0601132794 </F>
<F P=104>  Beijing XINHUA Domestic Service </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Chinese </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Beijing, 29 Dec (XINHUA) -- Namelist of removals of 
the National People's Congress [NPC] Standing Committee, adopted 
by the Fifth Session of the Eighth National People's Congress 
Standing Committee on 29 December 1993 
  Wu Fuzhao is hereby removed from the post of vice chairman 
of 
the Legislative Affairs Commission of the National People's 
Congress Standing Committee. 

